name atbegshi
category Package
revision 53051
shortdesc Execute stuff at \shipout time
longdesc This package is a modern reimplementation of package everyshi,
longdesc providing various commands to be executed before a \shipout
longdesc command. It makes use of e-TeX's facilities if they are
longdesc available. The package may be used either with LaTeX or with
longdesc plain TeX.
containersize 4748
