name bidi-atbegshi
category Package
revision 35154
shortdesc Bidi-aware shipout macros
longdesc The package adds some commands to the atbegshi package for
longdesc proper placement of background material in the left and right
longdesc corners of the output page, in both LTR and RTL modes. The
longdesc package only works with xelatex format and should be loaded
longdesc before the bidi package.
