name epstopdf-pkg
category Package
revision 53546
shortdesc Call epstopdf "on the fly"
longdesc The package adds support for EPS files in the graphicx package
longdesc when running under pdfTeX. If an EPS graphic is detected, the
longdesc package spawns a process to convert the EPS to PDF, using the
longdesc script epstopdf. This of course requires that shell escape is
longdesc enabled for the pdfTeX run.
