name etex-pkg
category Package
revision 41784
shortdesc E-TeX support package
longdesc The package provides support for LaTeX documents to use many of
longdesc the extensions offered by e-TeX; in particular, it modifies
longdesc LaTeX's register allocation macros to make use of the extended
longdesc register range. The etextools package provides macros that make
longdesc more sophisticated use of e-TeX's facilities.
