name everyhook
category Package
revision 35675
shortdesc Hooks for standard TeX token lists
longdesc The package takes control of the six TeX token registers
longdesc \everypar, \everymath, \everydisplay, \everyhbox, \everyvbox
longdesc and \everycr. Real hooks for each of the registers may be
longdesc installed using a stack like interface. For backwards
longdesc compatibility, each of the \everyX token lists can be set
longdesc without interfering with the hooks.
