name luatexbase
category Package
revision 52663
shortdesc Basic resource management for LuaTeX code
longdesc The LaTeX kernel (LaTeX2e 2015/10/01 onward) builds in support
longdesc for LuaTeX functionality, also available as ltluatex.tex for
longdesc users of plain TeX and those with older LaTeX kernel
longdesc implementations. This support is based on ideas taken from the
longdesc original luatexbase package, but there are interface
longdesc differences. This 'stub' package provides a compatibility layer
longdesc to allow existing packages to upgrade smoothly to the new
longdesc support structure.
