name memoir
category Package
revision 59610
shortdesc Typeset fiction, non-fiction and mathematical books
longdesc The memoir class is for typesetting poetry, fiction,
longdesc non-fiction, and mathematical works. Permissible document
longdesc 'base' font sizes range from 9 to 60pt. There is a range of
longdesc page-styles and well over a dozen chapter-styles to choose
longdesc from, as well as methods for specifying your own layouts and
longdesc designs. The class also provides the functionality of over
longdesc thirty of the more popular packages, thus simplifying document
longdesc sources. Users who wish to use the hyperref package, in a
longdesc document written with the memoir class, should also use the
longdesc memhfixc package (part of this bundle). Note, however, that any
longdesc current version of hyperref actually loads the package
longdesc automatically if it detects that it is running under memoir.
