name metapost-colorbrewer
category Package
revision 48753
shortdesc An implementation of the colorbrewer2.org colours for MetaPost
longdesc This package provides two MetaPost include files that define
longdesc all the colorbrewer2.org colours: colorbrewer-cmyk.mp
longdesc colorbrewer-rgb.mp The first defines all the colours as CMYK,
longdesc the second as RGB. Use whichever one you prefer. For an example
longdesc of what you can do, and a list of all the names, have a look at
longdesc colorbrewer-sampler.mp. You can also see the names on
longdesc http://colorbrewer2.org. The package also includes the Python
longdesc script used to generate the MP source from the colorbrewer
longdesc project.
