name psfrag
category Package
revision 15878
shortdesc Replace strings in encapsulated PostScript figures
longdesc Allows LaTeX constructions (equations, picture environments,
longdesc etc.) to be precisely superimposed over Encapsulated PostScript
longdesc figures, using your own favorite drawing tool to create an EPS
longdesc figure and placing simple text 'tags' where each replacement is
longdesc to be placed, with PSfrag automatically removing these tags
longdesc from the figure and replacing them with a user specified LaTeX
longdesc construction, properly aligned, scaled, and/or rotated.
