shortdesc Create images of dice with one, two, or three faces showing, using MetaPost
longdesc The package provides MetaPost code to create all possible
longdesc symmetrical views (up to rotation) of a right-handed die.
longdesc Configuration is possible by editing the source code, following
longdesc the guidance in the documentation.
