name ucharclasses
category Package
revision 58029
shortdesc Font actions in XeTeX according to what is being processed
longdesc The package takes care of switching fonts when you switch from
longdesc one Unicode block to another in the text of a document. This
longdesc way, you can write a document with no explicit font selection,
longdesc but a series of rules of the form "when entering block ...,
