name vtable
category Package
revision 51126
shortdesc Vertical alignement of table cells
longdesc The package allows vertical alignement of table cell by
longdesc providing: Z, L, C, R, J and I column types \nextRow and \lb
longdesc commands \setMultiColRow, \setMultiColumn, \setMultiRow and
longdesc \tableFormatedCell commands for tabular and similar
longdesc environment.
