name xeindex
category Package
revision 35756
shortdesc Automatic index generation for XeLaTeX
longdesc The package is based on XeSearch, and will automatically index
longdesc words or phrases in an XeLaTeX document. Words are declared in
longdesc a list, and every occurrence then creates an index entry whose
longdesc content can be fully specified beforehand.
