name zbmath-review-template
category Package
revision 59693
shortdesc Template for a zbMATH Open review
longdesc This package contains a template for zbMATH Open reviews. It
longdesc will show what your review will look like on zbMATH Open and
longdesc you can test whether your LaTeX-Code will compile on our
longdesc system. The template has to be compiled using XeLaTeX and
longdesc relies on scrartcl, scrlayer-scrpage, amsfonts, amssymb,
longdesc amsmath, babel, enumitem, etoolbox, fontspec, gensymb,
longdesc geometry, graphicx, mathrsfs, mathtools, stmaryrd, textcomp,
longdesc tikz-cd, xcolor, and xparse.
